data.description: This beautifully updated condo is in a gated community and conveniently located to so many surrounding areas in Jacksonville. This fabulous 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath end unit with a covered patio overlooking a private backyard with lake view. The kitchen features new SS appliances and granite countertops. Plantation shutters throughout. HVAC is 2017. Washer & dryer convey. 1 car garage with additional parking throughout the community. Condo fee includes internet, basic cable, security monitoring service, building insurance, and gate.
